<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>118</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa thisan a luong em?
 Ka Lalpa chu A thi'm?
 A luchang thiengtho chu A pie'm?
 Mantak loh kei tatna'n.

[V2]
 Nang hun neidi'n ei panpih in,
 Ginum a umzing di'n;
 Na Lalchutphah a Na chut tieng,
 Lalpa ei hezing in.

[V3]
 2. Kross a lungkhama A mauna,
 Kei gitloh ziek ahim?
 Hetphakloh A hehpih-na mak,
 Het guolloh hehpihna.

[V4]
 3. Nisa thimna a kisel in,
 A lopina a chawl;
 Thilsiem mihiem gilo sika,
 Siempa Krista thih in.

[V5]
 4. A Kross chu a hunglat laiin,
 Kenle ka mai sel ka;
 Ka lunggil kipak a dimin,
 Ka mitthi luong ina.

[V6]
 5. Hehpihna lei ka bat lungngaih,
 Mitthi'n dinzo puona;
 Lalpa ka hinna ka hun pie'i,
 Zie mai chu ka bawltheih.</lyrics>
<title>REMEMBER ME</title>
</song>